room_title: Escape room "Hunter's Revenge" by Locked & Coded in Charleston (WV)
review: This was such an awesome experience! We did the hunter's revenge room and finished with 10 minutes left. It was so fun and the staff was amazing! Puzzles were very well thought-out and just challenging enough. I'll definitely be back to try the Jail Break room!
